caption: Tried Mr. Klucker for the first time and it was AMAZING the klucker sauce and the jalapeño slaw make this chicken #Nashville Perfect. Can’t wait to try the Honeylicious.

I wish I could share photos of my delicious meal (next time) as I was to excited to dive into my yummy honeylicious chicken sandwich. It’s amazing!!!  I also ordered the chips and jalapeño coleslaw.  What a way to compliment and complete my meal. Definitely going to keep going back until I try everything on the menu. I’m sure it’s as good as what I had. Can’t wait!!!
OMG the honeylicious chicken sandwich is next level! The Beale street tea was on point too. I highly recommend this spot in river north Chicago!

I'll put it like this.... The honeylicious chicken sandwich was so good that I almost called the restaurant to send six more! On a serious note, I highly recommend the honeylicious chicken sandwich and the cajun house chips. To the restaurant, I look forward to meeting you all in person, happy new year!

Every single one of these chicken sandwiches are amazing and the jalapeño slaw is delicious. We also really enjoyed the Parmesan house made chips. We placed a large order for 30 nurses at work this weekend, and the food arrived on time, hot, packaged well, and everything was correct. I will definitely order from here again and me and my co-workers were all very satisfied with our lunch today. These sandwiches are huge as well, so most of us had some leftover for a nice afternoon snack as well.
arguably one of the best chicken sandwiches i’ve had in chicago!
